Strings:	
strored in heap(string obj) or String constant pool(scp)
immutable
Synchronization( multiple threads can access the string obj simultaniouly) 
Thread-safe
Less Efficient

StringBuffer:	
mutable
Heap
Synchronization( multiple threads can access the string obj simultaniouly) 
Thread-safe
Efficient

StringBuilder:	
mutable
Heap
non-synchornize (multiple threads can accesst the obj but not simultaniously.
non-Thread safe
more Efficient